Installing plugins:
		To build without certain plugins use --without-pluginname:
			./configure --without-flac --without-vorbis
		Currently available are mp3, aac, vorbis, and flac.
	./configure
	make
	make install

Enable the plugins in harp:
	harp -a
		select plugin management:
	admin> m
		add plugins:
	manage plugins> a
	Library (e.g., libharpmp3): libharpmp3
	manage plugins> a
	Library (e.g., libharpmp3): libharpaac
		...

Check that the plugins have been installed:
		list added plugins:
	manage plugins> l


Default Decoder libraries:
	libmpg123 - http://www.mpg123.de/

	faad2 - http://www.audiocoding.com/downloads.html
	mp4ff

	libvorbis - http://www.xiph.org/downloads/

	libflac - http://www.xiph.org/downloads/

Audio playback:
	ALSA - http://www.alsa-project.org
	OSS - http://opensound.com
